Pre-Game Insights: Oman will begin its 2024 T20 World Cup journey by taking on African side Namibia.
Aquib Ilyas named as the new captain for the ICC T20 World Cup 2024.
Oman could emerge as the dark horses of the groups who could end up giving a tough fight to the well-established opponents.
The squad is full of talent with former skipper Zeeshan Maqsood joining the team along with batting all-rounder Mohammed Nadeem.
